snippet.title: RunnerDot (PC) Gameplay - Score: 128 points
snippet.description:
Gameplay of the game RunnerDot, scoring 128 points.
The game is free for a limited time on Steam.
Just for the record, I won't play anymore.
I played only because it was free, there's a lot better and nicer free in browser games, for example.
To get the second achievement of the game, just set the game language to Czech.

RunnerDot 
Genre: Casual (?)
Platform: PC  
Developer: Ongakken s. r. o.
